Description:P0 casts Drain Life ({X}{1}{B}) at a 2/2 Grizzly Bears. With 6 Swamps the engine spends {X}{1}{B} at X=4, so Drain Life deals 4 to the Bears (it dies to lethal) but P0 gains only min(4, toughness 2) = 2 life — the cap is the creature's toughness before damage (mtg-624). NO "unimplemented effect 'StoreSVar'" warning.

